WEBVTT

00:05:27.707 --> 00:05:30.362
and there are like 100
of these lambs in the pen.

00:05:31.103 --> 00:05:34.553
And suddenly, this whole thing's starting
to feel like a German porno,

00:05:34.577 --> 00:05:35.892
and I'm like --

00:05:35.916 --> 00:05:38.469
(Laughter)

00:05:38.493 --> 00:05:42.050
Melanie picks up the lamb,
puts it on the post, opens it up.

00:05:42.074 --> 00:05:43.341
Albert hands me the knife.

00:05:43.365 --> 00:05:45.064
I go in, tail comes off.

00:05:45.088 --> 00:05:48.194
I go in, I grab the scrotum,
tip comes off.

00:05:48.218 --> 00:05:50.564
Albert instructs, "Push it way up there."

00:05:50.588 --> 00:05:51.739
I do.

00:05:51.763 --> 00:05:52.914
"Push it further."

00:05:52.938 --> 00:05:54.089
I do.

00:05:54.113 --> 00:05:57.388
The testicles emerge. They look
like thumbs, coming right at you.

00:05:57.412 --> 00:05:59.031
And he says, "Bite 'em.

00:05:59.055 --> 00:06:01.035
Just bite 'em off."